                    እንዘ፡ ዕራቁ፤</dc:title><crm:P102_has_title rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7090QeneLagassa/title/t1" xml:lang="gez"/><dc:title xml:lang="gez">La-gaṣṣa gafāʾi tǝsaffǝh manṭolāʿta rǝtʿ marʾawe tawlāṭ Krǝstos gǝfuʿ ʾǝnza ʿǝrāqu (Qǝne possibly of the mawaddǝs-type)</dc:title><dc:title xml:lang="en">You spread out in the face of the oppressor the veil of uprightness, the Groom of Change, Christ, oppressed while naked…</dc:title><dc:source rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/UppQ1524o"/></rdf:Description><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7090QeneLagassa"><lawd:hasAttestation rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/UppQ1524o"/></rdf:Description><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7090QeneLagassa"><saws:isAttributedToAuthor rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14574GabraLeul"/></rdf:Description><oa:Annotation rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7090QeneLagassa/person/annotation/1"><oa:hasTarget rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7090QeneLagassa"/><oa:hasBody rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14574GabraLeul"/><oa:annotatedAt rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date">2026-04-05+02:00</oa:annotatedAt><lawd:hasName>Gabra Lǝʿul</lawd:hasName></oa:Annotation><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7090QeneLagassa/title/t1"><rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/E35_Title"/><rdfs:label>ለገጸ፡ ገፋኢ፡ ትሰፍህ፡ 
